    Class Description
    Bullet

    Container

    Entity
    Base Class all other Objects are based off Handles collision, Screenpositioning
    GameObject
    Base Class of all GameObjects GameObjects can spawn in Rooms
    Layer
    Layer Class Each Layer can have one image/animation An Object can have several layers
    NPC
    Base NPC Class All the Enemies are based off this class Deals with Pathfinding
    RectangleF
    Abstract rectangle with float precision attributes
    Sprite
    Sprite directly extends the Entity class adds Sprites or animation to the Entity loads all the Animation
